column2: SELECT     m.Objid, m.Ra AS ra1, m.Dec AS dec1,    n.objid, n.ra, n.dec, n.petroMag_u, n.petroMagErr_u, n.petroMag_g, n.petroMagErr_g, n.petroMag_r,    n.petroMagErr_r, n.petroMag_i, n.petroMagErr_i, n.petroMag_z, n.petroMagErr_z, n.nChild, n.clean,    petroFlux_u, petroFlux_g, petroFlux_r, petroFlux_i, petroFlux_z, petroFluxIvar_u, petroFluxIvar_g,   petroFluxIvar_r, petroFluxIvar_i, petroFluxIvar_z,    o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.lowmassmag from MyDB.lowmass AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
